Invocation Name: eyes workout
des:
Practice yoga for eyes with Alexa every day to keep or improve your keen eyesight.

Just ask Alexa to start eyes workout and do exercises one by one with relaxed music in background. Say "Next" once you've finished an exercise, or "Repeat" - to repeat current one. Do not be distracted by the screen or anything else during the exercises.
